GIRL1AU.original: ~z~You're gonna get burnt one day too, you know. And don't you dare come crying to me when it happens.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你总有一天也会引火烧身的，到时出事了你也不敢来找我哭诉。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Oh my god! He just pushed her. Is she dead?
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~哦天哪！被他推下来了。她死了吗？

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Yeah. I'll think about how crazy you were.
~z~Shit, Luis, why do I love you so bad?
~z~You just took an overdose over a guy who ain't seen you in twelve months. Fuck, girl.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~为了个一年没见面的男人，你就想服药自尽。你有病吧，姑娘。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~But, seriously, I just don't want to marry you.
~z~Okay? I don't care which it is, just get over here, please.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~好吗？怎么样都无所谓，你过来吧，求你了。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~I think a rat just bit me.
~z~Did you get the book I sent you?
~z~I've been watching you, you know. I know all about those other girls.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~我一直都看着你，知道吗。我知道你有多少女友。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~I think I just saw a murder.
~z~Now come on, get down from there.
~z~I got to get you to a hospital. There's one in Easton.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~我这就送你去医院，Easton就有一家。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Yeah. Look, I've had a lot going on.
~z~What's wrong with you? Nothing apart that you're mentally deranged.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你哪里不好？当然是因为你脑子有问题。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~You really fucking care. I knew it!
~z~There's nothing mixed about this - stay away from me!
~z~That was the most beautiful thing anyone's ever done for me. Imagine what our kids will think of this story.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~这真是我人生中的高光时刻啊。想象下咱们的孩子听到这故事时会怎么想。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Will you think of me after I'm gone?
~z~Aren't you coming in? You could hold back my hair when they pump me.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你不来吗？洗胃的时候你可以帮我收下头发。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~No dumbass, that's just your liver failing.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~错了，傻逼，是你的肝脏衰竭了。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~No, I mean I'm sorry we can't be together. You can't have me.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~不，我是为我们无法在一起道的歉。你无法拥有我。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~You got to stop doing this. One of these days you actually gonna succeed in killing yourself.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你得住手了，不然哪天你就害了自己。
~z~大力神门口？这里是男同夜店啊。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~This is more painful than I thought it would be.
~z~Get in there. You the doctor's problem now.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~进去吧。让医生为你头疼去吧。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Okay, wait - just - I - I just don't want to marry you.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~好吗？等下，我、我只是不想娶你。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Kill that sick pervert. Rip him apart.
~z~Don't catch a cold. Stay sane and stay the fuck away from me. Bye!
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~别感冒了。正常点，离我他妈的远点。再见！
~z~里面写着是你把我推下去的。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Nothing. Nothing. Come on, come on, get over here.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~没啥，没啥。拜托，赶紧的，过来吧。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~I was just... just... meeting someone! A date, actually.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~我只是...来见个人！其实是约会。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Yeah! You a serious Grade A nut job.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~是啊！你他妈是一等一的疯子。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~You fuck people and then you ignore them. That's easy. It's a game, isn't it?
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你操完逼了就拍屁股走人，真轻松啊。像游戏一样，不是吗？

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Y-your dad? Look, he probably was. Okay, but, if you'll excuse me, I-I gotta go.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你爸？应该是没说错。行了，不好意思，我要走了。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Hey Margot. How - how are you? What are you doing here?
~z~Yeah, that tends to be what happens when you take a massive overdose. Shit.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~对，服药过量是这样子的。妈的。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~I'm going to die, and it's all your fault.
~z~You hadn't noticed falling in that river? You crazier than I thought.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你也不看看会掉到河里去吗？你真是比我想的还要疯狂。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~It's Tony, isn't it? He warned you off me.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~都是Tony，对吧？他让你离我远点的。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~There's a note in my apartment that explains all about you and why I did this.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~我公寓里有份笔记，记录了你的情况和我寻死的原因。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Hold on to yourself, bitch. It would be real inconvenient if you died on me.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你自己抱去，贱人。死在我这儿就不好办了。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~You know, my dad was right about you.

GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~对。拒绝向来是对事不对人的。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Rest assured I ain't coming anywhere near you. Wrap up warm now.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~别想了，我不会贴上来的。自个裹紧实点。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Fuck the police. Make this guy pay.
~z~Oh, hi, Luis. Wow, what a coincidence.
~z~No, you killed yourself, You're the selfish one here, bitch.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~不，是你害了自己。你才是那个自私的人，贱逼。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Fuck! You've killed me, you thoughtless fucking asshole.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~操！你早把我杀了，没头没脑的混账。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Hey, don't apologize. I love keeping people from killing themselves. It's a weird fetish of mine.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~嘿，别道歉。我只是喜欢救下自杀者。算是个奇怪的癖好吧。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~You know that? You think you're such hot shit, don't you?
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你懂吗？你以为自己是个大红人，对吧？

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~or naming stars after me, or whatever. It's nothing personal.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~还是给我买星星，都不管用。对事不对人的。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~It's meant to go to the papers if I die.
~z~Perfect. I can't wait to be demonised in the press. Now I got another reason to save your ass.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~太棒了。马上我就是薄情寡义的渣男了。又多了一个救你的理由。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~I'll be dead soon. Either get me to the hospital or I'm dead.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~我快不行了。要是不送我去医院，我就死了。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~What's wrong with me, Luis? At least tell me why I'm not good enough for you.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~我哪里不好了，Luis？至少告诉我我哪里配不上你啊。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~You can't get away with that shit.
~z~We ain't having kids, Margot. I'm dropping you over there and then I ain't seeing you ever again.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~咱没有孩子，Margot。送你到那，咱就再也不见了。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~It's... It was a long time ago. I mean, it's time to move on.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~那...那是很久以前的事了。我是说，也该向前看了。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~And no matter how many letters you send me, or chocolate bunnies,
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~不管你给我寄多少封信，送多少巧克力兔，

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Of course I care. I don't want no one killing themselves.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~我当然在乎。我不想任何人了断自己。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~You don't care about anyone. You're a shell.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你不在乎别人。你空有一副躯壳。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Oh fuck. I thought I'd just pass out.
~z~Tone don't even know you exist. Breaking things off was my own good judgement.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~Tone都不知道你是谁。一刀两断是我自己思考的结果。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~ I just took 37 painkillers and 15 sleeping pills.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~我刚吞下了37片止痛药和15片安眠药。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~If you loved me, you'd save me.
~z~What's time got to do with anything?
~z~I see enough bulimic bitches at the club, Margot. You on your own.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~天天催吐的娘们我在店里见多了，Margot。你自己去。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~I don't want to marry someone who is a complete psychopath.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~只是不想娶一个十足的精神病。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Are you going to start taking me seriously now?
~z~Can you just understand that what we had was nothing. Shit.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~你明不明白咱俩是成不了的？妈的。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~it - it was over a year ago.
~z~When you suddenly decided the view was better from there?
~z~How can you be so nice one second and mean the next. You're sending mixed signals.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~刚刚还好好的，怎么就变卦了，你真让人捉摸不透。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Either that, or I'd think I was.
~z~No. Listen, Margot, you're a nice girl, and it was nice hooking up with you, but
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~没有。听着，Margot，你是个好人，和你约会也很开心，但...

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Now you starting to understand. Thank you!
~z~When I die, people will blame you.
~z~The only thing going near that mouth is the tube for the stomach pump.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~待会儿来吻你的东西，只有那根洗胃管。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Okay? Maybe I'm empty, like you said. Or maybe, like pretty much every man alive,
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~好吗？也许我确实是一具空壳。但也许，我跟大多数男人一样，

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~I never made no promises to you. You need to forget about me.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~喂，我可没跟你订婚。赶紧忘了我好吗。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~Don't tell me you were just passing through.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~别告诉我你是碰巧路过这里。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~You going to hospital, you idiot. Shit.
~z~I think I can feel my heart breaking, baby.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~我好像能感受到心脏在碎裂，宝贝。

GIRL1AU.original: ~z~thinking of me as being crazy. It must help.
GIRL1AU.translated: ~z~把我当成疯婆娘。没有负罪感。
